overview:
The Swap it! Encrypt it! file transfer service is an alternative to sending large email attachments that would otherwise require an FTP, CDS or DVDS, USB flash drive or expensive courier.

Businesses, organizations and students use the Swap it! Encrypt it! file sharing service to transfer, receive and track files. Easily and securely send large files without the need of e-mail attachments, an FTP or installing software, directly from your e-mail. Use Swap it! Encrypt it! to share programs, documents, video, music, photos or anything!

Swap it! Encrypt it! set out to create the first no contract file sharing service that offered users unlimited downloads and free functions that other companies over charge for. Less then two years later and Swap it! Encrypt it! has accomplished this goal as well as managed to build a system that is completely unique and intuitive.
